nodes.text: Longnose and Scarcheek were the nicknames given by Jaina Solo to the two hit-Squibs who tried to kill her on Tenupe. He revealed that Emala, Sligh, and Grees were the heads of the family and his great-great-great grandparents. When Jaina told the Mollom to let them go, they took it literally and flung the two hit-Squibs onto the Chiss' island with their trebuchets.
